Pre-Game Insights: Thierry Mouyouma and his team landed at Durban airport on Monday at 6h30 and are set to face Lesotho on Tuesday, October 15, 2024, at 14h TU (15h Gabon time) at the Moses Mabhida Stadium.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Gabon team had three false departures (13h, 18h, and 22h) before finally leaving Franceville on Sunday at 23h30.
Others: The match is part of the 4th day of the eliminatory phase of the 2025 Africa Cup of Nations in Morocco.
